narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned how to perform research and read and write a scientific paper.
I have gained a ton of insight into how a laboratory functions as well as how to design my own experiment.
Designing a research project, writing a proposal, working in a lab, attending lab meetings, analyzing data.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I think maybe I could have started designing my experiment earlier and thus got to work on it earlier, but overall I think the way it has been going has been good.
It would be great to have a bit more info and direction about completing the senior requirement before senior year.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Well, its required if you want a B.S.
